---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Sashiko Techniques & Getting Started"
  description="Learn how to get started with sashiko embroidery. Guides on stitching techniques, choosing needles, thread, and pattern paper for beginners."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-warm py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-marketing text-center">
      <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Coming Soon</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-6">
        Sashiko Techniques
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your comprehensive guide to sashiko embroidery. From choosing the right tools 
        to mastering traditional stitching techniques.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Coming Soon Content -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-marketing max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose-custom">
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We're working on comprehensive guides to help you master sashiko embroidery. 
          Check back soon for detailed tutorials and recommendations on:
        </p>
        
        <!-- Topic Grid -->
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
          <!-- Getting Started -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Getting Started
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Everything you need to know to begin your sashiko journey, from basic supplies to your first stitches.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Needles -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-terracotta-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Sashiko Needles
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Understanding different needle types and how to choose the right one for your project.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Thread -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Thread Selection
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Traditional sashiko thread vs alternatives, colors, and how thread weight affects your work.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pattern Paper -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Pattern Transfer
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Methods for transferring patterns to fabric, including sashiko transfer paper and alternatives.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Stitching Techniques -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-terracotta-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Stitching Techniques
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Master the running stitch, learn proper spacing, and discover tips for clean corners and curves.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Beginner Patterns -->
          <div class="bg-cream-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-lg text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
              Beginner Patterns
            </h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-600 text-sm">
              Our recommended patterns for beginners, starting simple and building to more complex designs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Newsletter Signup -->
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-serif font-semibold text-xl text-charcoal-900 mb-3">
            Get Notified
          </h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-600 mb-6">
            Sign up to be notified when we publish new technique guides and tutorials.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-500 italic">
            Newsletter signup coming soon
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-cream-100">
    <div class="container-marketing text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-4">
        Ready to Start Stitching?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Browse our pattern library and create your first sashiko design today.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/patterns" class="btn-primary">
          Browse Patterns
        </a>
        <a href="/design" class="btn-outline">
          Open Design Tool
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
